wikipedia_page.main: Patrick James Grieshaber (born 24 November 1996) is an English cricketer who most recently played for Gloucestershire and made his first-class debut as a righthanded batsman and wicketkeeper in 2014. On 24 July 2016 he made his List A debut against Sussex in the 2016 Royal London One-Day Cup.Grieshaber was released by Gloucestershire at the end of the 2017 season.
